      "title": "More than 1.5 million litres of fuel released today - LIOC",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "With the early opening of the Trincomalee terminal, Lanka IOC says it has released more than 1.5 million litres of petrol and diesel in more than 100 fuel bowsers today (10).",
        "LIOC Managing Director Mr. Manoj Gupta said all dealers have been advised to ensure priority for ambulances.",
        "He requested for the earnest cooperation of the general public for this purpose."
      ],
